Note: The Serviceguard Manager Plug-in is not vulnerable.

RESOLUTION

HP has provided Serviceguard Manager and Java JDK/JRE upgrades to resolve these vulnerabilities.
The Serviceguard Manager upgrade is available from the following location:

URL: http://www.hp.com/go/softwaredepot/ha

The Java JDK/JRE upgrade is available from the following location

URL: http://www.hp.com/go/Java

